    description:
      "<p style='margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:16px; color:rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family:&quot;Avenir Next&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;'><font size='3' style='font-family:inherit;'>Population Density is the concentration of people in a specific area. It helps to quantify demography. The map used to create the app uses the Global Human Settlement Layer (GHSL) created by the European Commission. The map is visualized based on population density (persons per square mile) between latitudes at one degree intervals. A second layer that situates global cities based on population overlays the population density layer and allows the user to look at the cities that contributed to the population density in the latitude zones.</font></p><p style='margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:16px; color:rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family:&quot;Avenir Next&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;'><font size='3' style='font-family:inherit;'>Search for a location to learn more about the latitude zone it is located in and other global cities in the same zone. Use one of these search methods:</font></p><ul><li><font size='3' style='font-family:inherit;'>Click the search box and type in an address or choose <strong>Use current location</strong></font></li><li><font size='3' style='font-family:inherit;'>Click within the map</font></li><li><font size='3' style='font-family:inherit;'>Use the <strong>Draw a Zone</strong> tool to draw a polygon in the map</font></li></ul><p style='margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:16px; color:rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family:&quot;Avenir Next&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;'><font size='3' style='font-family:inherit;'>Results will include information about the latitude zone and other global cities. The results can be <strong>exported into a CSV</strong> or can be shared using the <strong>Screenshot</strong> tool. Use the <strong>Filter</strong> tool to filter the map by hemisphere and latitude zones!</font></p><p style='margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:16px; color:rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family:&quot;Avenir Next&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;'><font size='2' style='font-family:inherit;'><b>Data Source:</b> <a href='https://ghsl.jrc.ec.europa.eu/index.php' style='color:rgb(0, 121, 193); text-decoration-line:none; font-family:&quot;Avenir Next&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;' target='_blank' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'>GHSL, European Commission</a></font></p>",
